{
  "video_id": "MvXZzKZ3JYQ",
  "title": "Architecture that's built to heal | Michael Murphy",
  "es": 1,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13995.0,
      "end_time": 16896.0,
      "text": "Every weekend for as long as I can remember,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17746.0,
      "end_time": 19953.0,
      "text": "my father would get up on a Saturday,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20597.0,
      "end_time": 22443.0,
      "text": "put on a worn sweatshirt"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23163.0,
      "end_time": 24318.0,
      "text": "and he&#39;d scrape away"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24342.0,
      "end_time": 27165.0,
      "text": "at the squeaky old wheel of a house that we lived in."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27681.0,
      "end_time": 29469.0,
      "text": "I wouldn&#39;t even call it restoration;"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 29493.0,
      "end_time": 31427.0,
      "text": "it was a ritual, catharsis."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31906.0,
      "end_time": 35266.0,
      "text": "He would spend all year scraping paint with this old heat gun"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 35290.0,
      "end_time": 36534.0,
      "text": "and a spackle knife,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 36558.0,
      "end_time": 38635.0,
      "text": "and then he would repaint where he scraped,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 38659.0,
      "end_time": 41280.0,
      "text": "only to begin again the following year."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 41520.0,
      "end_time": 44118.0,
      "text": "Scraping and re-scraping, painting and repainting:"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 44688.0,
      "end_time": 47632.0,
      "text": "the work of an old house is never meant to be done."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 49589.0,
      "end_time": 52921.0,
      "text": "The day my father turned 52, I got a phone call."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 52945.0,
      "end_time": 54367.0,
      "text": "My mother was on the line"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 54391.0,
      "end_time": 58129.0,
      "text": "to tell me that doctors had found a lump in his stomach --"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 58153.0,
      "end_time": 60172.0,
      "text": "terminal cancer, she told me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 60196.0,
      "end_time": 62790.0,
      "text": "and he had been given only three weeks to live."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 64269.00000000001,
      "end_time": 67790.0,
      "text": "I immediately moved home to Poughkeepsie, New York,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 67814.0,
      "end_time": 70222.0,
      "text": "to sit with my father on death watch,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 70246.0,
      "end_time": 72637.0,
      "text": "not knowing what the next days would bring us."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 73529.0,
      "end_time": 74896.0,
      "text": "To keep myself distracted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 74920.0,
      "end_time": 76674.0,
      "text": "I rolled up my sleeves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 76698.0,
      "end_time": 80603.0,
      "text": "and I went about finishing what he could now no longer complete --"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 80627.0,
      "end_time": 83180.0,
      "text": "the restoration of our old home."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 83666.0,
      "end_time": 86707.0,
      "text": "When that looming three-week deadline came"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 86731.0,
      "end_time": 87889.0,
      "text": "and then went,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 87913.0,
      "end_time": 89544.0,
      "text": "he was still alive."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 89904.0,
      "end_time": 91386.0,
      "text": "And at three months,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 91410.0,
      "end_time": 92576.0,
      "text": "he joined me."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 92901.0,
      "end_time": 95576.0,
      "text": "We gutted and repainted the interior."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 95600.0,
      "end_time": 98893.0,
      "text": "At six months, the old windows were refinished,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 98918.0,
      "end_time": 100213.0,
      "text": "and at 18 months,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 100237.0,
      "end_time": 102886.0,
      "text": "the rotted porch was finally replaced."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 103575.0,
      "end_time": 105403.0,
      "text": "And there was my father,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 105427.0,
      "end_time": 108680.0,
      "text": "standing with me outside, admiring a day&#39;s work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 108704.0,
      "end_time": 111256.0,
      "text": "hair on his head, fully in remission,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 111727.0,
      "end_time": 113961.0,
      "text": "when he turned to me and he said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 113985.0,
      "end_time": 115142.0,
      "text": "\"You know, Michael,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 115166.0,
      "end_time": 117115.0,
      "text": "this house saved my life.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 118967.0,
      "end_time": 123360.0,
      "text": "So the following year, I decided to go to architecture school."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 124167.0,
      "end_time": 125317.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 125929.0,
      "end_time": 129490.0,
      "text": "But there, I learned something different about buildings."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 129729.99999999999,
      "end_time": 130703.99999999999,
      "text": "Recognition seemed to come"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 130728.00000000001,
      "end_time": 134279.0,
      "text": "to those who prioritized novel and sculptural forms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 134303.0,
      "end_time": 136775.0,
      "text": "like ribbons, or ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 137514.0,
      "end_time": 138673.0,
      "text": "pickles?"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 138697.0,
      "end_time": 141600.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 142866.0,
      "end_time": 145357.0,
      "text": "And I think this is supposed to be a snail."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 146530.0,
      "end_time": 148264.0,
      "text": "Something about this bothered me."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 148971.0,
      "end_time": 152914.0,
      "text": "Why was it that the best architects, the greatest architecture --"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 152938.0,
      "end_time": 155540.0,
      "text": "all beautiful and visionary and innovative --"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 156780.0,
      "end_time": 158249.0,
      "text": "is also so rare,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 158273.0,
      "end_time": 160720.0,
      "text": "and seems to serve so very few?"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 161715.0,
      "end_time": 163212.0,
      "text": "And more to the point:"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 163236.0,
      "end_time": 166691.0,
      "text": "With all of this creative talent, what more could we do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 168556.0,
      "end_time": 170865.0,
      "text": "Just as I was about to start my final exams,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 170889.0,
      "end_time": 173589.0,
      "text": "I decided to take a break from an all-nighter"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 174180.0,
      "end_time": 176930.0,
      "text": "and go to a lecture by Dr. Paul Farmer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 177514.0,
      "end_time": 180510.0,
      "text": "a leading health activist for the global poor."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 180534.0,
      "end_time": 184316.0,
      "text": "I was surprised to hear a doctor talking about architecture."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 184340.0,
      "end_time": 186822.0,
      "text": "Buildings are making people sicker, he said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 186846.0,
      "end_time": 188639.0,
      "text": "and for the poorest in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 188663.0,
      "end_time": 191559.0,
      "text": "this is causing epidemic-level problems."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 191918.0,
      "end_time": 193553.0,
      "text": "In this hospital in South Africa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 193577.0,
      "end_time": 195761.0,
      "text": "patients that came in with, say, a broken leg,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 195785.0,
      "end_time": 198381.0,
      "text": "to wait in this unventilated hallway,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 198405.0,
      "end_time": 202932.0,
      "text": "walked out with a multidrug-resistant strand of tuberculosis."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 203294.0,
      "end_time": 206918.0,
      "text": "Simple designs for infection control had not been thought about,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 206942.0,
      "end_time": 209460.0,
      "text": "and people had died because of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 210140.0,
      "end_time": 213164.0,
      "text": "\"Where are the architects?\" Paul said."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 213692.0,
      "end_time": 215693.0,
      "text": "If hospitals are making people sicker,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 215717.0,
      "end_time": 217621.0,
      "text": "where are the architects and designers"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 217645.0,
      "end_time": 222255.0,
      "text": "to help us build and design hospitals that allow us to heal?"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 224486.0,
      "end_time": 226125.0,
      "text": "That following summer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 226150.0,
      "end_time": 228952.0,
      "text": "I was in the back of a Land Rover with a few classmates,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 228976.0,
      "end_time": 232457.0,
      "text": "bumping over the mountainous hillside of Rwanda."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 232964.0,
      "end_time": 236933.0,
      "text": "For the next year, I&#39;d be living in Butaro in this old guesthouse,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 236957.0,
      "end_time": 240154.0,
      "text": "which was a jail after the genocide."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 240967.0,
      "end_time": 244888.0,
      "text": "I was there to design and build a new type of hospital"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 244912.0,
      "end_time": 247106.0,
      "text": "with Dr. Farmer and his team."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 247965.0,
      "end_time": 250990.0,
      "text": "If hallways are making patients sicker,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 250123.0,
      "end_time": 253876.0,
      "text": "what if we could design a hospital that flips the hallways on the outside,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 253901.0,
      "end_time": 256219.0,
      "text": "and makes people walk in the exterior?"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 256243.0,
      "end_time": 258612.0,
      "text": "If mechanical systems rarely work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 258636.00000000003,
      "end_time": 261219.00000000003,
      "text": "what if we could design a hospital that could breathe"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 261243.0,
      "end_time": 263119.0,
      "text": "through natural ventilation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 263143.0,
      "end_time": 266284.0,
      "text": "and meanwhile reduce its environmental footprint?"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 266309.0,
      "end_time": 268865.0,
      "text": "And what about the patients&#39; experience?"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 268889.0,
      "end_time": 271205.0,
      "text": "Evidence shows that a simple view of nature"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 271229.0,
      "end_time": 273388.0,
      "text": "can radically improve health outcomes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 273752.0,
      "end_time": 275814.0,
      "text": "So why couldn&#39;t we design a hospital"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 275838.0,
      "end_time": 278551.0,
      "text": "where every patient had a window with a view?"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 278575.0,
      "end_time": 283986.0,
      "text": "Simple, site-specific designs can make a hospital that heals."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 284764.0,
      "end_time": 286547.0,
      "text": "Designing it is one thing;"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 286571.0,
      "end_time": 288797.0,
      "text": "getting it built, we learned, is quite another."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 289619.0,
      "end_time": 292303.0,
      "text": "We worked with Bruce Nizeye,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 292327.0,
      "end_time": 293840.0,
      "text": "a brilliant engineer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 293864.0,
      "end_time": 295988.0,
      "text": "and he thought about construction differently"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 296120.0,
      "end_time": 297868.0,
      "text": "than I had been taught in school."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 298458.0,
      "end_time": 300782.0,
      "text": "When we had to excavate this enormous hilltop"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 300806.0,
      "end_time": 303741.0,
      "text": "and a bulldozer was expensive and hard to get to site,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 303765.0,
      "end_time": 306284.0,
      "text": "Bruce suggested doing it by hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 306309.0,
      "end_time": 309983.0,
      "text": "using a method in Rwanda called \"Ubudehe,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 310700.0,
      "end_time": 312556.0,
      "text": "which means \"community works for the community.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 313820.0,
      "end_time": 316406.0,
      "text": "Hundreds of people came with shovels and hoes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 317800.0,
      "end_time": 318794.0,
      "text": "and we excavated that hill"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 318819.0,
      "end_time": 322428.0,
      "text": "in half the time and half the cost of that bulldozer."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 323328.0,
      "end_time": 326268.0,
      "text": "Instead of importing furniture, Bruce started a guild,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 326292.0,
      "end_time": 328698.0,
      "text": "and he brought in master carpenters to train others"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 328723.0,
      "end_time": 330477.0,
      "text": "in how to make furniture by hand."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 330501.0,
      "end_time": 332700.0,
      "text": "And on this job site,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 332950.0,
      "end_time": 335584.0,
      "text": "15 years after the Rwandan genocide,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 336326.0,
      "end_time": 339931.0,
      "text": "Bruce insisted that we bring on labor from all backgrounds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 339955.0,
      "end_time": 341866.0,
      "text": "and that half of them be women."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 342302.0,
      "end_time": 344947.0,
      "text": "Bruce was using the process of building to heal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 344971.0,
      "end_time": 346956.0,
      "text": "not just for those who were sick,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 346980.0,
      "end_time": 349678.0,
      "text": "but for the entire community as a whole."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 351860.0,
      "end_time": 355941.0,
      "text": "We call this the locally fabricated way of building, or \"lo-fab,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 355965.0,
      "end_time": 358320.0,
      "text": "and it has four pillars:"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 358984.0,
      "end_time": 360157.0,
      "text": "hire locally,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 360182.0,
      "end_time": 361617.0,
      "text": "source regionally,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 362111.0,
      "end_time": 363531.0,
      "text": "train where you can"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 363555.0,
      "end_time": 365119.0,
      "text": "and most importantly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 365143.0,
      "end_time": 368705.0,
      "text": "think about every design decision as an opportunity"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 368729.0,
      "end_time": 372645.0,
      "text": "to invest in the dignity of the places where you serve."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 373219.0,
      "end_time": 376490.0,
      "text": "Think of it like the local food movement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 376730.0,
      "end_time": 377428.0,
      "text": "but for architecture."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 377741.0,
      "end_time": 379943.0,
      "text": "And we&#39;re convinced that this way of building"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 379968.0,
      "end_time": 381906.0,
      "text": "can be replicated across the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 381930.0,
      "end_time": 386477.0,
      "text": "and change the way we talk about and evaluate architecture."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 387405.0,
      "end_time": 389207.0,
      "text": "Using the lo-fab way of building,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 389231.0,
      "end_time": 393270.0,
      "text": "even aesthetic decisions can be designed to impact people&#39;s lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 393762.0,
      "end_time": 396464.0,
      "text": "In Butaro, we chose to use a local volcanic stone"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 396488.0,
      "end_time": 398516.0,
      "text": "found in abundance within the area,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 398540.0,
      "end_time": 400577.0,
      "text": "but often considered a nuisance by farmers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 400601.0,
      "end_time": 402330.0,
      "text": "and piled on the side of the road."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 402671.0,
      "end_time": 405155.0,
      "text": "We worked with these masons to cut these stones"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 405179.0,
      "end_time": 408369.0,
      "text": "and form them into the walls of the hospital."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 408394.0,
      "end_time": 410591.0,
      "text": "And when they began on this corner"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 410615.0,
      "end_time": 413703.0,
      "text": "and wrapped around the entire hospital,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 414283.0,
      "end_time": 416805.0,
      "text": "they were so good at putting these stones together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 416829.0,
      "end_time": 420441.0,
      "text": "they asked us if they could take down the original wall and rebuild it."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 420465.0,
      "end_time": 422753.0,
      "text": "And you see what is possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 423467.0,
      "end_time": 424700.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s beautiful."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 425794.0,
      "end_time": 427673.0,
      "text": "And the beauty, to me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 427697.0,
      "end_time": 430915.0,
      "text": "comes from the fact that I know that hands cut these stones,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 431435.0,
      "end_time": 434420.0,
      "text": "and they formed them into this thick wall,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 434444.0,
      "end_time": 438434.0,
      "text": "made only in this place with rocks from this soil."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 440107.0,
      "end_time": 444208.0,
      "text": "When you go outside today and you look at your built world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 444973.0,
      "end_time": 446154.0,
      "text": "ask not only:"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 446178.0,
      "end_time": 449404.0,
      "text": "\"What is the environmental footprint?\" -- an important question --"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 449428.0,
      "end_time": 450702.0,
      "text": "but what if we also asked,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 450726.0,
      "end_time": 454382.0,
      "text": "\"What is the human handprint of those who made it?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 455427.0,
      "end_time": 459710.0,
      "text": "We started a new practice based around these questions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 459950.0,
      "end_time": 461644.0,
      "text": "and we tested it around the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 462467.0,
      "end_time": 463618.0,
      "text": "Like in Haiti,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 463642.0,
      "end_time": 468241.0,
      "text": "where we asked if a new hospital could help end the epidemic of cholera."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 468755.0,
      "end_time": 470394.0,
      "text": "In this 100-bed hospital,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 470418.0,
      "end_time": 472930.0,
      "text": "we designed a simple strategy"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 472117.0,
      "end_time": 476577.0,
      "text": "to clean contaminated medical waste before it enters the water table,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 476601.0,
      "end_time": 478609.0,
      "text": "and our partners at Les Centres GHESKIO"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 478633.0,
      "end_time": 481162.0,
      "text": "are already saving lives because of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 481187.0,
      "end_time": 482382.0,
      "text": "Or Malawi:"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 482406.0,
      "end_time": 485635.0,
      "text": "we asked if a birthing center could radically reduce"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 485659.0,
      "end_time": 487558.0,
      "text": "maternal and infant mortality."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 487892.0,
      "end_time": 491145.0,
      "text": "Malawi has one of the highest rates of maternal and infant death"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 491169.0,
      "end_time": 492385.0,
      "text": "in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 492410.0,
      "end_time": 495733.0,
      "text": "Using a simple strategy to be replicated nationally,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 495757.0,
      "end_time": 497977.0,
      "text": "we designed a birthing center"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 498100.0,
      "end_time": 500308.0,
      "text": "that would attract women and their attendants"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 500333.0,
      "end_time": 504166.0,
      "text": "to come to the hospital earlier and therefore have safer births."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 504569.0,
      "end_time": 506243.0,
      "text": "Or in the Congo, where we asked"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 506267.0,
      "end_time": 508515.0,
      "text": "if an educational center could also be used"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 508539.0,
      "end_time": 510721.0,
      "text": "to protect endangered wildlife."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 510745.0,
      "end_time": 512330.0,
      "text": "Poaching for ivory and bushmeat"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 512354.00000000006,
      "end_time": 515901.00000000006,
      "text": "is leading to global epidemic, disease transfer and war."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 515924.0,
      "end_time": 519146.0,
      "text": "In one of the hardest-to-reach places in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 519171.00000000006,
      "end_time": 522970.00000000006,
      "text": "we used the mud and the dirt and the wood around us"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 522121.0,
      "end_time": 523784.0,
      "text": "to construct a center"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 523808.0,
      "end_time": 528557.0,
      "text": "that would show us ways to protect and conserve our rich biodiversity."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 529526.0,
      "end_time": 531131.0,
      "text": "Even here in the US,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 531155.0,
      "end_time": 532418.0,
      "text": "we were asked to rethink"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 532442.0,
      "end_time": 536504.0,
      "text": "the largest university for the deaf and hard of hearing in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 536844.0,
      "end_time": 539100.0,
      "text": "The deaf community, through sign language,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 539124.0,
      "end_time": 541534.0,
      "text": "shows us the power of visual communication."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 541558.0,
      "end_time": 543810.0,
      "text": "We designed a campus that would awaken the ways"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 543834.0,
      "end_time": 545882.0,
      "text": "in which we as humans all communicate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 545907.0,
      "end_time": 547826.0,
      "text": "both verbally and nonverbally."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 549729.0,
      "end_time": 552263.0,
      "text": "And even in Poughkeepsie, my hometown,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 552986.0,
      "end_time": 555826.0,
      "text": "we thought about old industrial infrastructure."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 556196.0,
      "end_time": 557473.0,
      "text": "We wondered:"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 557497.0,
      "end_time": 562600.0,
      "text": "Could we use arts and culture and design to revitalize this city"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 562840.0,
      "end_time": 564705.0,
      "text": "and other Rust Belt cities across our nation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 564730.0,
      "end_time": 567694.0,
      "text": "and turn them into centers for innovation and growth?"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 568121.0,
      "end_time": 571550.0,
      "text": "In each of these projects, we asked a simple question:"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 572450.0,
      "end_time": 574223.0,
      "text": "What more can architecture do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 574681.0,
      "end_time": 576606.0,
      "text": "And by asking that question,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 576630.0,
      "end_time": 580372.0,
      "text": "we were forced to consider how we could create jobs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 580396.0,
      "end_time": 582806.0,
      "text": "how we could source regionally"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 582831.0,
      "end_time": 586570.0,
      "text": "and how we could invest in the dignity of the communities"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 586810.0,
      "end_time": 587312.0,
      "text": "in which we serve."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 587959.0,
      "end_time": 589205.0,
      "text": "I have learned"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 589943.0,
      "end_time": 594497.0,
      "text": "that architecture can be a transformative engine for change."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 597117.0,
      "end_time": 599790.0,
      "text": "About a year ago, I read an article"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 600567.0,
      "end_time": 604711.0,
      "text": "about a tireless and intrepid civil rights leader"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 605328.0,
      "end_time": 606634.0,
      "text": "named Bryan Stevenson."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 608423.0,
      "end_time": 612420.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 614249.0,
      "end_time": 617433.0,
      "text": "And Bryan had a bold architectural vision."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 617983.0,
      "end_time": 620572.0,
      "text": "He and his team had been documenting"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 620596.0,
      "end_time": 624240.0,
      "text": "the over 4,000 lynchings of African-Americans"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 624264.0,
      "end_time": 626524.0,
      "text": "that have happened in the American South."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 626889.0,
      "end_time": 631699.0,
      "text": "And they had a plan to mark every county where these lynchings occurred,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 631723.0,
      "end_time": 635112.0,
      "text": "and build a national memorial to the victims of lynching"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 635136.0,
      "end_time": 636826.0,
      "text": "in Montgomery, Alabama."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 637879.0,
      "end_time": 640976.0,
      "text": "Countries like Germany and South Africa"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 641880.0,
      "end_time": 643490.0,
      "text": "and, of course, Rwanda,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 643730.0,
      "end_time": 646145.0,
      "text": "have found it necessary to build memorials"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 646169.0,
      "end_time": 649800.0,
      "text": "to reflect on the atrocities of their past,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 649320.0,
      "end_time": 652200.0,
      "text": "in order to heal their national psyche."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 652440.0,
      "end_time": 655212.0,
      "text": "We have yet to do this in the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 656679.0,
      "end_time": 663314.0,
      "text": "So I sent a cold email to info@equaljusticeintiative.org:"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 663338.0,
      "end_time": 665286.0,
      "text": "\"Dear Bryan,\" it said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 666102.0,
      "end_time": 667738.0,
      "text": "\"I think your building project"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 667762.0,
      "end_time": 670717.0,
      "text": "is maybe the most important project we could do in America"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 670741.0,
      "end_time": 673731.0,
      "text": "and could change the way we think about racial injustice."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 674640.0,
      "end_time": 676624.0,
      "text": "By any chance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 676648.0,
      "end_time": 678569.0,
      "text": "do you know who will design it?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 678593.0,
      "end_time": 680222.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 680784.0,
      "end_time": 682511.0,
      "text": "Surprisingly, shockingly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 683547.0,
      "end_time": 684861.0,
      "text": "Bryan got right back to me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 684885.0,
      "end_time": 688930.0,
      "text": "and invited me down to meet with his team and talk to them."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 688763.0,
      "end_time": 690815.0,
      "text": "Needless to say, I canceled all my meetings"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 690839.0,
      "end_time": 693179.0,
      "text": "and I jumped on a plane to Montgomery, Alabama."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 693203.0,
      "end_time": 694361.0,
      "text": "When I got there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 694797.0,
      "end_time": 698281.0,
      "text": "Bryan and his team picked me up, and we walked around the city."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 698305.0,
      "end_time": 700632.0,
      "text": "And they took the time to point out"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 700656.0,
      "end_time": 703676.0,
      "text": "the many markers that have been placed all over the city"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 703701.0,
      "end_time": 706145.0,
      "text": "to the history of the Confederacy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 706169.0,
      "end_time": 710396.0,
      "text": "and the very few that mark the history of slavery."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 710420.0,
      "end_time": 712247.0,
      "text": "And then he walked me to a hill."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 712828.0,
      "end_time": 714329.0,
      "text": "It overlooked the whole city."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 714934.0,
      "end_time": 717164.0,
      "text": "He pointed out the river and the train tracks"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 717188.0,
      "end_time": 719883.0,
      "text": "where the largest domestic slave-trading port in America"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 719907.0,
      "end_time": 721910.0,
      "text": "had once prospered."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 721115.0,
      "end_time": 722733.0,
      "text": "And then to the Capitol rotunda,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 722757.0,
      "end_time": 724829.0,
      "text": "where George Wallace had stood on its steps"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 724853.0,
      "end_time": 727737.0,
      "text": "and proclaimed, \"Segregation forever.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 728205.0,
      "end_time": 730560.0,
      "text": "And then to the very hill below us."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 730800.0,
      "end_time": 733397.0,
      "text": "He said, \"Here we will build a new memorial"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 733421.0,
      "end_time": 737863.0,
      "text": "that will change the identity of this city and of this nation.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 738855.0,
      "end_time": 742309.0,
      "text": "Our two teams have worked together over the last year"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 742333.0,
      "end_time": 743975.0,
      "text": "to design this memorial."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 747184.0,
      "end_time": 750500.0,
      "text": "The memorial will take us on a journey"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 750836.0,
      "end_time": 753910.0,
      "text": "through a classical, almost familiar building type,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 753934.0,
      "end_time": 758590.0,
      "text": "like the Parthenon or the colonnade at the Vatican."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 758994.0,
      "end_time": 760321.0,
      "text": "But as we enter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 760345.0,
      "end_time": 764306.0,
      "text": "the ground drops below us and our perception shifts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 764330.0,
      "end_time": 768424.0,
      "text": "where we realize that these columns evoke the lynchings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 768448.0,
      "end_time": 770478.0,
      "text": "which happened in the public square."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 771500.0,
      "end_time": 772321.0,
      "text": "And as we continue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 772345.0,
      "end_time": 775440.0,
      "text": "we begin to understand the vast number"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 775464.0,
      "end_time": 778457.0,
      "text": "of those who have yet to be put to rest."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 778481.0,
      "end_time": 783186.0,
      "text": "Their names will be engraved on the markers that hang above us."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 784202.0,
      "end_time": 788271.0,
      "text": "And just outside will be a field of identical columns."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 788973.0,
      "end_time": 792771.0,
      "text": "But these are temporary columns, waiting in purgatory,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 792796.0,
      "end_time": 796619.0,
      "text": "to be placed in the very counties where these lynchings occurred."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 798124.0,
      "end_time": 800496.0,
      "text": "Over the next few years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 800520.0,
      "end_time": 802506.0,
      "text": "this site will bear witness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 803600.0,
      "end_time": 805298.0,
      "text": "as each of these markers is claimed"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 805322.0,
      "end_time": 807581.0,
      "text": "and visibly placed in those counties."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 808258.0,
      "end_time": 813426.0,
      "text": "Our nation will begin to heal from over a century of silence."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 815799.0,
      "end_time": 817852.0,
      "text": "When we think about how it should be built,"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 817876.0,
      "end_time": 820675.0,
      "text": "we were reminded of Ubudehe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 820700.0,
      "end_time": 823680.0,
      "text": "the building process we learned about in Rwanda."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 823562.0,
      "end_time": 826106.0,
      "text": "We wondered if we could fill those very columns"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 826130.0,
      "end_time": 830290.0,
      "text": "with the soil from the sites of where these killings occurred."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 831218.0,
      "end_time": 834382.0,
      "text": "Brian and his team have begun collecting that soil"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 834940.0,
      "end_time": 837724.0,
      "text": "and preserving it in individual jars"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 837748.0,
      "end_time": 841207.0,
      "text": "with family members, community leaders and descendants."
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 841890.0,
      "end_time": 844992.0,
      "text": "The act of collecting soil itself"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 846148.0,
      "end_time": 848818.0,
      "text": "has lead to a type of spiritual healing."
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 849545.0,
      "end_time": 852310.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s an act of restorative justice."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 852844.0,
      "end_time": 855398.0,
      "text": "As one EJI team member noted"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 855422.0,
      "end_time": 859474.0,
      "text": "in the collection of the soil from where Will McBride was lynched,"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 860231.0,
      "end_time": 863364.0,
      "text": "\"If Will McBride left one drop of sweat,"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 863388.0,
      "end_time": 864743.0,
      "text": "one drop of blood,"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 865173.0,
      "end_time": 866576.0,
      "text": "one hair follicle --"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 866964.0,
      "end_time": 868585.0,
      "text": "I pray that I dug it up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 868609.0,
      "end_time": 871584.0,
      "text": "and that his whole body would be at peace.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 874683.0,
      "end_time": 877944.0,
      "text": "We plan to break ground on this memorial later this year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 877968.0,
      "end_time": 882413.0,
      "text": "and it will be a place to finally speak of the unspeakable acts"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 882437.0,
      "end_time": 884292.0,
      "text": "that have scarred this nation."
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 886380.0,
      "end_time": 892241.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 897245.0,
      "end_time": 900682.0,
      "text": "When my father told me that day that this house --"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 900706.0,
      "end_time": 901861.0,
      "text": "our house --"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 901885.0,
      "end_time": 903900.0,
      "text": "had saved his life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 903970.0,
      "end_time": 905282.0,
      "text": "what I didn&#39;t know"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 905306.0,
      "end_time": 908558.0,
      "text": "was that he was referring to a much deeper relationship"
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 908582.0,
      "end_time": 911220.0,
      "text": "between architecture and ourselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 911649.0,
      "end_time": 914995.0,
      "text": "Buildings are not simply expressive sculptures."
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 915190.0,
      "end_time": 919117.0,
      "text": "They make visible our personal and our collective aspirations"
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 919141.0,
      "end_time": 920298.0,
      "text": "as a society."
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 921177.0,
      "end_time": 924417.0,
      "text": "Great architecture can give us hope."
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 925162.0,
      "end_time": 927536.0,
      "text": "Great architecture can heal."
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 928478.0,
      "end_time": 929694.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 929719.0,
      "end_time": 936990.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}